{"talk":{"id":69384,"name":"Nimisha Jain: The joy of shopping -- and how to recapture it online","description":"Shopping is about more than just what you buy: it's a treasure hunt to discover something new, a negotiation to get a great deal, a time to catch up with friends and family. But for many, online shopping has turned the experience into an impersonal, unsatisfactory event. Is there a way to bring back the magic? With exciting examples from companies in India, Thailand and China, consumer expert Nimisha Jain introduces us to \"conversational commerce,\" a new retail model that combines the convenience of a digital experience with the personalized touch of a real, human interaction.","slug":"nimisha_jain_the_joy_of_shopping_and_how_to_recapture_it_online","recorded_at":"2020-10-21 00:00:00","published_at":"2021-01-26 15:45:07","updated_at":"2021-01-27 15:12:46","viewed_count":0,"emailed_count":0,"event":{"id":655,"name":"TED@BCG"},"images":[{"image":{"size":"113x85","url":"https:\/\/pe.tedcdn.com\/images\/ted\/2ebf2f9ef26b50b64fd3ca47e0a40717724c1ea4_113x85.jpg"}},{"image":{"size":"240x180","url":"https:\/\/pe.tedcdn.com\/images\/ted\/2ebf2f9ef26b50b64fd3ca47e0a40717724c1ea4_240x180.jpg"}},{"image":{"size":"615x461","url":"https:\/\/pe.tedcdn.com\/images\/ted\/2ebf2f9ef26b50b64fd3ca47e0a40717724c1ea4_615x461.jpg"}},{"image":{"size":"2400x1800","url":"https:\/\/pe.tedcdn.com\/images\/ted\/2ebf2f9ef26b50b64fd3ca47e0a40717724c1ea4_2400x1800.jpg"}}],"image_16x9":"https:\/\/pe.tedcdn.com\/images\/ted\/bedae0215c44297cbe352da49ea026cd23701dad_2880x1620.jpg","media":{"internal":{"64k":{"uri":"https:\/\/download.ted.com\/talks\/NimishaJain_2020S-64k.mp4?apikey=c692baa7dafbf74e4fbde1ac88b44cafc96cfe7a","filesize_bytes":5632037,"mime_type":"video\/mp4"},"180k":{"uri":"https:\/\/download.ted.com\/talks\/NimishaJain_2020S-180k.mp4?apikey=c692baa7dafbf74e4fbde1ac88b44cafc96cfe7a","filesize_bytes":15586019,"mime_type":"video\/mp4"},"320k":{"uri":"https:\/\/download.ted.com\